{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water and 1 Tbsp salt in mixing bowl. Place Varoma dish into position and weigh in asparagus. Cover Varoma then steam <b>16 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>.","Remove Varoma, place asparagus under cold running water then drain and set aside. Discard steaming water.","Place chilli, onions and oil in mixing bowl then chop <b>3 sec\/speed 6<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then sauté <b>2 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add vinegar, lime juice, sugar, pepper and ½ tsp salt then mix <b>10 sec\/speed 3<b>.","Cut cooked asparagus into pieces (approx. 3 cm) then add to mixing bowl.","Add mangoes, endive and mint then transfer to a large bowl and mix gently with spatula. Divide between serving plates then top with smoked goose breast before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["500 g water","1 Tbsp fine sea salt, plus ½ tsp","800 g asparagus, lower stems peeled","1 fresh chilli, halved, deseeded","100 g red onions, quartered","30 g sunflower oil","20 g white wine vinegar","20 g lime juice","½ tsp sugar","¼ tsp ground black pepper","500 g ripe mangoes, cut in pieces (3 cm)","100 g curly endive, cut in pieces (5 cm)","2 sprigs fresh mint, leaves only","160 g smoked goose breast, skin on, sliced (5 mm)"]}],"id":"r432802","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-f951dj5UoS0\/XZMuLutf2dI\/AAAAAAAAaCM\/myBCZxdmox8unqK2fKslbUCRNT4k0oo1gCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_C7--9QobKlrf_r-X.png","title":"Asparagus and Mango Salad","publishedAt":"2019-04-01T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"16 g","fat":"17 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"21 g","calories":"1332 kJ \/ 318 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large bowl","basicInfo":["medium","15m","35m","4 portions"]}